l evolution of EXLup showed\nthat, although vertical mixing should be stronger during the outburst than in\nthe quiescent phase, fast radial transport of crystals (e.g., by stellar/disk\nwind) was required to reproduce the observed mid-infrared spectra.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Oct 2011 18:30:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
