ckreaction effects, induced by the radiation pressure, that alter\nthe dynamics of the mean displacement of the mirror, and we argue this\nbackreaction can be ignored for a slowly moving mirror.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2011 09:08:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
